<p>There is no point in creating a <code>const</code> reference to a literal numeric value. Most likely the intent was not to create a reference, but
a constant value.</p>
<h2>Noncompliant Code Example</h2>
<pre>
const int &amp; weekdayCount = 7;  // Noncompliant
</pre>
<h2>Compliant Solution</h2>
<pre>
const int weekdayCount = 7;
</pre>